      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPING CHEBET (1) is a capable type and proved too strong last time to win by 8 lengths at this track in a handy 29.94 beating Coolhand Sue. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in her latest win. Can continue the winning form. BEAUTIFUL CHILD (3) jumped from a low draw and boxed on well to finish third last time, beaten 2 lengths (25.55) behind Cheeky Belgin at Q Lakeside. Bold showing expected. DON'T YOU THINK (7) is an honest type who is new here. Fast away and led throughout to score a one length win over 457m at Q Lakeside (26.04). Won at her only start from this box. Expected to feature again. BROWN BREAD (2) is building a nice picket fence and can add to the tally.",
